article.headline: Leach's 22 lead Fairfield over Iona 68-63 in MAAC Tournament quarterfinal

images.name: Iona Gaels vs. Fairfield Stags: Game Highlights

article.linkText: Leach's 22 lead Fairfield over Iona 68-63 in MAAC Tournament quarterfinal
article.story: ATLANTIC CITY, N.J. -- — Jalen Leach had 22 points in Fairfield's 68-63 win over Iona on Wednesday night in the Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference Tournament quarterfinal. No. 2 seed Fairfield will play on Friday against the winner of the Thursday quarterfinal between Marist and Niagara. Leach added eight rebounds and four steals for the Stags (21-11). Caleb Fields added 20 points and seven rebounds. Brycen Goodine finished with nine points. Jeremiah Quigley had 14 points, 10 rebounds and five assists for the seventh-seeded Gaels (15-16, 1-1). Joel Brown added 13 points and three steals for Iona. Idan Tretout also had 11 points. Fairfield went into the half leading Iona 34-31. Fields scored nine points in the half. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
